    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey so i was out for a run in stanley park and i totally wiped out. my left ankle is huge right now and it's super swollen. i cant really walk on it without a lot of pain but i dont think i want to go to the emergency room lol. do u think i can just do the RICE thing for a few days and be fine?",
