      "content": "i hear u but the er is gonna take like 8 hours and cost a fortune. i think it's probably just a bad sprain since i didn't hear a pop or anything when i fell. if i just keep it elevated and use ice aggressively for like 3-4 days, isn't that basically what a doctor would tell me to do anyway? it'll definitely feel better by then right?",
