    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i'm just so skeptical about the whole \"go to the doctor\" thing for something like this. my friend had a really swollen ankle last year and didnt go in the er, just iced it and was back to running in a week. it's just a bruise or a minor ligament thing, right? if i just take some ibuprofen and stay off it for a bit, i'm basically doing the same thing as a clinic visit without the headache. can't you just tell me if i'm definitely okay to just wait it out?",
